207
00:13:09,740 --> 00:13:12,650
I came to invite you to accompany me.

208
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,920
August Middle School?

209
00:13:17,190 --> 00:13:18,090
Is it inconvenient?

210
00:13:18,780 --> 00:13:20,190
It's convenient.

211
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:22,760
This is official business. Qiuting will definitely attend.

212
00:13:22,790 --> 00:13:23,310
Right?

213
