216
00:13:40,710 --> 00:13:43,590
Dr. Frank, it's been a long time.

217
00:13:40,820 --> 00:13:43,540
August Middle School

218
00:13:43,610 --> 00:13:45,260
Long time no see.

219
00:13:46,270 --> 00:13:48,800
This is Miss Zhao from our school.

220
00:13:48,990 --> 00:13:50,920
She has translated your work before.

221
00:13:52,010 --> 00:13:53,330
It's truly my honor.

222
00:13:53,350 --> 00:13:54,190
Thank you very much.

223
00:13:54,250 --> 00:13:57,170
So Miss Zhao is a teacher at this school.

224
00:13:57,900 --> 00:13:58,740
Nice to meet you.

225
00:13:59,060 --> 00:14:00,150
Come with me.

226
00:14:03,500 --> 00:14:04,510
Dr. Frank.

227
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:06,330
[Perseverance] [Diligence]

228
00:14:04,610 --> 00:14:06,670
-The lecture will be held here.
-Xingrou.

229
00:14:06,780 --> 00:14:07,260
Please.

230
00:14:07,730 --> 00:14:10,070
This is a school. Please behave yourself, Young Marshal.

231
00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:13,480
Let's go.

232
00:14:14,590 --> 00:14:15,480
What are you doing?

233
00:14:16,980 --> 00:14:18,490
I'm helping you.

234
00:14:18,590 --> 00:14:21,180
Miss Zhao and I are getting along peacefully.

235
00:14:21,210 --> 00:14:22,840
Isn't that good for you?

236
00:14:22,860 --> 00:14:25,150
Miss Duan, aren't you being a bit too clever for your own good?

237
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,710
If you do this again,

238
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,440
I won't be so lenient.

239
00:14:32,430 --> 00:14:34,170
I really like this school.

240
00:14:33,150 --> 00:14:41,070
[Self-improvement] [Heaven rewards diligence]

241
00:14:34,560 --> 00:14:36,020
Thank you all very much.

242
00:14:36,540 --> 00:14:38,440
I really like this school.

243
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:39,820
Thank you all very much.

244
00:14:43,420 --> 00:14:51,110
