245
00:14:44,530 --> 00:14:47,040
Thank you very much, Dr. Frank,

246
00:14:47,070 --> 00:14:49,590
for delivering this lecture to us.

247
00:14:49,610 --> 00:14:51,800
And many thanks to Miss Zhao for her translation.

248
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:55,820
Of course,

249
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:58,540
we are also very grateful to the daughter of Chief Duan,

250
00:14:58,690 --> 00:14:59,900
Miss Duan Jinyao,

251
00:14:59,920 --> 00:15:01,650
for making this lecture possible.

252
00:15:01,680 --> 00:15:03,470
Please, Miss Duan, come up and say a few words.

253
00:15:01,990 --> 00:15:08,630
[Self-improvement] [Heaven rewards diligence]

254
00:15:08,950 --> 00:15:10,150
I am honored

255
00:15:10,170 --> 00:15:12,300
to be able to contribute to the cause of education.

256
00:15:12,580 --> 00:15:15,420
I am also pleased that our country has women like Miss Zhao,

257
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:17,230
who are such outstanding career women.

258
00:15:17,990 --> 00:15:19,000
I believe

259
00:15:19,020 --> 00:15:21,920
that women should break free from the constraints of traditional thinking

260
00:15:22,310 --> 00:15:26,230
and not limit their lives to being wives and mothers.

261
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:29,040
Miss Zhao, do you agree?

262
00:15:31,040 --> 00:15:31,940
I agree.

263
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:38,370
Then may I ask, are you single now?

264
00:15:53,740 --> 00:15:54,540
I am single.
